{"tid":1983364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伍公子&林慧韡 同 大J 既分別(2015)","createTime":"2020-04-21T19:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T04:09:19.000Z","uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8598e36e58bc0c13b79347b5506ef1050fd0a973","tid":1983364,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:01:20.000Z","msg":"伍公子：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">《網絡挑機》事敗 伍公子：YouTuber全部收檔都唔關我事<br />\n192,908 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?list=LL-lrKOuGhB1aRA6e7spVdkQ&amp;index=2431&amp;v=iNGu_TF8zqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Flist%3DLL-lrKOuGhB1aRA6e7spVdkQ%26index%3D2431%26v%3DiNGu_TF8zqQ&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8qbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=81d8ac11\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?list=LL-lrKOuGhB1aRA6e7spVdkQ&amp;index=2431&amp;v=iNGu_TF8zqQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大J<br />\n<blockquote>不過另一網絡紅人大 J（ YouTube訂閱人數超過 35萬），亦曾獲邀拍攝節目，但他卻醒目推方丈。上週六（ 5日）大 J同胡杏兒一齊出席活動，大 J表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">無綫之前有個節目搵我，不過我推咗，因為我覺得網民先係我嘅觀眾，電視機我唔係有太大興趣。</span>（<span style=\"color: gold;\">覺唔覺今次班 YouTuber輸曬？</span>）<span style=\"color: red;\">某程度上係㗎，佢哋可能社會經驗唔夠，咁好容易被人呃到，佢哋被 TVB過咗一『棟』，佢哋係輸咗㗎，希望網民唔好放棄網絡人啦，又希望中咗招嘅網絡人下次學精啲!</span>」你冇中招，真係叻到裂！<br />\n大 J仲唔小心踩埋一眾網絡女神：「<span style=\"color: red;\">好老實講，有啲網友被人話女神，佢哋一上到電視機拍埋真正藝人側邊時候，你會見到分別好大。</span>」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林慧韡：<br />\n<blockquote>一眾平時鬧爆大台嘅 YouTuber，今次被方丈玩番轉頭，據知大台原本想搵埋人氣高嘅達哥（林慧韡）同熊仔頭幫手，好在佢哋冇埋堆執身彩。<span style=\"color: gold;\">本刊問回兩位當事人，一向敢言嘅達哥就話</span>：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我要諗諗做唔做呢個訪問，不過呢個問題涉及好多嘢比較複雜。</span>」<br />\n而熊仔頭就話：「有冇搵我唔知，（想唔想拍大台節目？）𠵱家就唔識答喇，之前都仲答到。」<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩位平時牙尖嘴利嘅網絡紅人，見到網民狠批同驚得罪方丈，都罕有地「慎言」，明白嘅。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/206890585-冇機挑-拒上《網絡挑機》-大j：佢地好易俾人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftvb4life.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F206890585-%E5%86%87%E6%A9%9F%E6%8C%91-%E6%8B%92%E4%B8%8A%E3%80%8A%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E6%8C%91%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%8B-%E5%A4%A7j%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A2%E5%9C%B0%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%93%E4%BF%BE%E4%BA%BA&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8qbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=563df845\" target=\"_blank\">https://tvb4life.pixnet.net/blog/post/206890585-冇機挑-拒上《網絡挑機》-大j：佢地好易俾人</a>"},{"pid":"829e28bf3c68f0f11f291ae0315d620cfd36352b","tid":1983364,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:24:37.000Z","msg":"點評3位YouTuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公子選手：<br />\n有抗爭 意志（爆seed）<br />\n冇抗爭 意識（堅持理念）<br />\n敢作先鋒（上TVB、反送中文宣）<br />\n獲得<code>掌聲</code><br />\n<br />\n爆機選手：<br />\n明哲保身<br />\n「識時務者許冠傑」<br />\n堅持理念（寧投白票 不表態度）<br />\n獲得 最多<code>獎金</code><br />\n<br />\n巨龍選手：<br />\n冇乜「社會性」朋友<br />\n無忘初心（「因為我覺得網民先係我嘅觀眾」）<br />\n開無雙挑機，能進能退（面對網戰、面對黑警）<br />\n獲得<code>獎全</code>和 最多<code>掌聲</code>"},{"pid":"e277d62a62484ffc2ed14e7273efca3487104825","tid":1983364,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T20:23:07.000Z","msg":"一個繼續去咗完美世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46eb78a1ab713a9a0633b07f9f0cc17f38b3e8b7","tid":1983364,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e277d62a62484ffc2ed14e7273efca3487104825","tid":1983364,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T20:23:07.000Z","msg":"一個繼續去咗完美世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T22:21:12.000Z","msg":"Search資料途中發現<br />\n原來 林慧韡 一向縮骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始有D體諒佢<br />\n今次反送中唔表態（投白票）<br />\n<blockquote>本刊問回兩位當事人，一向敢言嘅達哥就話：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我要諗諗做唔做呢個